query:
SELECT s.id, s.siteNumber, s.floorLevelId, fl.levelName 
FROM sites s 
LEFT JOIN floor_levels fl ON s.floorLevelId = fl.id 
WHERE s.centreId = (SELECT id FROM shopping_centres WHERE name = 'Highlands Marketplace') 
ORDER BY s.siteNumber;
